<div class="hidden" id="aboutUs">
	<div class="about-header">
		<div class="container">
			<h3>About Us</h3>
			<p class="attn">we like the internet.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-half profile">
				<%= image_tag "trudy.png", :class => 'profile-pic' %>
				<h4>Trudy MacNabb</h4>
				<p>Trudy is a passionate back-end developer. She is an active member of the development community. When she is not busy learning she enjoys teaching others as a lead mentor at Hacker You and instructor with Ladies Learning Code. Trudy has also set out to share her passion for Ruby on Rails as one of the organizers of Rails Girls Toronto. When she is not building the internet she is exploring her interest in dance parties, tomatoes, and public transportation.</p>
			</div>
			<div class="col-half profile">
				<%= image_tag "jordan.png", :class => 'profile-pic' %>
				<h4>Jordan Deutsch</h4>
				<p>Jordan is a front-end developer and internet admirer. As a recent transplant to Toronto she has enjoyed immersing herself in the burgeoning tech community. When she is not behind a computer screen she loves to share her enthusiasm for programming with others as a lead instructor for Ladies Learning Code and mentor at Hacker You and Node School Toronto. She moonlights as a coffee enthusiast, amateur commuter biker, and yoga student.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="quote">
		<div class="container">
			<p>Up at Five. Second coffee at noon. In bed by nine.</p>
		</div>
	</div>
	<%= render template: 'contact/contact'%>
</div>
<script>
	$(document).on('ready page:load',function(){
	    $('#aboutUs').fadeIn(1000);
	});
</script>
